DarkMouse::
She saw he was noticing her nervousness. She decided to play it 
off. "Look pal, mice don't fly. If we were ment to fly, the matrix 
would have given up wings. So let's just hurry up. The sooner we get 
there, the sooner I can get my paws back on the ground. Got it?"
She tried to just hide her fear untill she could get a better handle 
on what was going on.
